Let's make ObjectMapper a class level constant. Jackson documentation mentions constructing an ObjectMapper has non-trivial overhead and is able to create lightweight, thread-safe reader and writers from itself.
private static final ObjectMapper MAPPER;

static {
  MAPPER = new ObjectMapper();
  SerializationUtil.configureMapper(MAPPER);
}

